{"word":"G4100 - πιστεύω - pisteúō - pist-yoo'-o - Believe","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πιστεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pisteúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pist-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Believe</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"நம்புதல் - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to believe"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis/4102\">G4102</a>; to <i>have faith</i> (in, upon, or with respect to, a person or thing), that is, <i>credit</i>; by implication to <i>entrust</i> (especially one&rsquo;s spiritual well being to Christ): - believe (-r), commit (to trust), put in trust with.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3640/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G4100/4100\">G4100</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102/4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103/4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104/4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569/569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570/570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571/571\">G571</a>"}]}